snippet.title: Diablo III Eternal Collection - Announcement Video - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
What’s a little gift between friends? Join Reggie and CEO of Blizzard, Mike Morhaime, as they talk about the complete #DiabloSwitch experience coming this fall.

Learn more about Diablo III Eternal Collection for Nintendo Switch!
https://goo.gl/c6D9gT

#NintendoSwitch #DiabloIII
